How to Install
--------------

Firefox: Download GreaseMonkey addon and browse to the raw version of this script. Install and you're done.

Opera: Place this file somewhere locally and then browse to:
       Settings -> Preferences -> Advanced -> Content -> JavaScript Options -> User JavaScript folder
       Add the folder where the user script resides

Chrome: If your version of Chrome supports extension, browse to the raw version of this script. Install as an Extension and you're done.
